      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:c118c3258c8cd529",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "mega trend, I don't know, rise of private markets right.",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 990,
        "char_end": 1046,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 61720,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 64440,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0004 - BlackRock_s Rob Goldstein on the Next Megatrends in Finance_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:c31cbe1114ff5792",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The current technological wave, particularly AI, is creating an urgent demand within the finance industry for involvement and integration.",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.03
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:80706cf53ca0e26d",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "we're in this new sort of technological wave with AI.",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 1627,
        "char_end": 1680,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 91800,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 94479,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0004 - BlackRock_s Rob Goldstein on the Next Megatrends in Finance_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:06e6a0d84c577e8e",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "It very much feels like everyone in professional finance wants",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 1691,
        "char_end": 1753,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 94720,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 98360,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0004 - BlackRock_s Rob Goldstein on the Next Megatrends in Finance_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:fad68867f32e6834",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "there's this like urgency. Yeah, and there's a perennial question",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 2234,
        "char_end": 2299,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 118039,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 121160,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0004 - BlackRock_s Rob Goldstein on the Next Megatrends in Finance_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:6ffe43384496f0cc",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Financial institutions are actively preparing to integrate historical data into AI models, indicating a strategic shift towards leveraging advanced analytics.",
        "episode_id": "4cec22d8-717e-46c6-ab87-b43b01512ecb",
        "grounded": false,
        "insight_type": "fact"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e37bc89881b1c5dc",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "A key debate exists regarding the true productivity and utility of AI in finance, distinguishing between genuine technological advancement and trend-chasing by management.",
